des:
Ask Birmingham Watering Holes for help choosing your next meeting spot

Alexa will provide an ideal suggestion by asking a series of questions and giving you an answer.

To start, just say "Alexa, launch Birmingham Watering Holes" or "Alexa, open Birmingham Watering Holes" to get started".

At any time, you can stop by saying "Alexa, stop"
